## Update an existing rat [PUT /rats/{id}]

Change the values of an existing rat

Scope: public

+ Parameters
  + id: `56a78141f9fbac397a27ab3e` (integer, required) - ID of the rat to update

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + platform: `xb` (string) - Changing the platform of the rat to Xbox 1

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + links (Link) - Links
        + data (Rat) - The rat that was just modified
